        <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-blue-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0">▶</span><span><strong>J on premium squares:</strong> J on DLS = 16 points, J on TLS = 24 points from one tile. JO reaching a premium square can score 17+ points from two letters.</span></li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-blue-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0">▶</span><span><strong>JO is your safety play:</strong> At 9 points for two letters, JO guarantees a decent score even in the worst board position. Never exchange J when JO is available.</span></li>
